      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/bofa-s-hartnett-warns-froth-is-building-in-us-stocks-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的迈克尔哈特内特表示，美国股市和加密货币的强劲上涨导致这些资产类别出现泡沫。]]></description>
